specmurt- don't worry so much about it.  this patch will work with the x3 game that I put up on piratebay, so if you downloaded that, this will work with it.

don't update x3 from any other website and you should be fine with the program that's available from this site.

if you're running leopard you may have to find yourself a work around, such as installing + patching on the previous OS, then copying it to the new one. (one computer to another is the only current workaround)
